data.description: If you are looking for peace and quiet with land - or even just looking for a new home for you and all of your little furry friends- then this 2.23-acre home is perfect for you. This property includes a tornado shelter, 2 shops, a storage building, 3 car ports, a fenced chicken coop, even a storage for your generator and your lawnmower. Did i mention the covered patio spaces?! YES there is tons of space throughout the home. Come and check it out!
